latestPosts.caption:
I hate you Chat GPT for this, 
because you ate my whole day to love my improved #ghibli style images❤️

Story: so after seeing this new and lovely trend, I wanted to try this out for my pictures.
But, I had to install chat gpt for this, so I did.
Later I found and realised that I need to get a plus (paid) version of this and this is not that simple what I am seeing on Instagram.🙁
But why would I pay to create few images where I don’t use any AI too especially chat gpt!
Ummm I’ve added the prompt as explained by others, but the app denied to process,
🗣️ Due to over request, app is not able to, you can add some details to get a similar image.
Was getting such replies,
Meanwhile seeing the Instagram feed loaded with ghibli,
🕵🏻 Umm I decided bhai ab to kar k hi rahungi,
So I added a different prompt for my ghibli portrait,
Say Hey chat GPT, can you please create a ghibli style art /image of ____ you have explain about you and your some very noticeable and identifying details showing in the pic you want to convert.
Eg: the way you look, pose, walk or facial expression.
Then enter the text and within few seconds you’ll get your ghibli style portrait! Woohoo 
You can create 1-2 image only in a day , so play wisely, 
That’s how I made my portraits, and it took three days ugh 

More other apps are there, but let me tell you frankly you are going to waste your time.
So if the chat GPt is not applying it on your photo, just add the prompt I said above. ✨
